### This file can be used with the "REST Client" extension in VS Code.
### Just click "Send Request" above each endpoint to test it!

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api


### 1. GENERATE CONTENT
POST {{baseUrl}}/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "AI in Digital Marketing",
  "platform": "LinkedIn",
  "audience": "Marketing Professionals"
}

### 

### 2. MARKETING ASSISTANT (ASK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What are 3 ways to improve organic reach on Instagram in 2026?"
}

###

### 3. GENERATE VIRAL IDEAS
POST {{baseUrl}}/ideas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "Sustainable fashion brands"
}

###

### 4. IMPROVE CONTENT
POST {{baseUrl}}/improve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Check out our new shoes. They are very cool and made of recycled materials. Buy them now on our website."
}
